Package: libmodule-build-pm-filter-perl
Architecture: any
Depends: perl, libmodule-build-perl, libfile-copy-recursive-perl
Description: Add a PM source filter to Module::Build
 This module add support for source code filter to Module::Build. It derive
 from the Module::Build class and overload several methods from it.
